definitions.text:
@chung tình
* verb
- To love only one person, to be steadfast in love

@chung chạ
- To share everything in everyday life
-To share bed and board

@chung chung
- Very vague, unspecific
=kết luận chung chung+a very vague conclusion

@chung đụng
- To rub shoulders with
=không thích sống chung đụng với những người không tốt+to be loath to rub shoulders with bad people

@chung thẩm
- To exercise final jurisdiction
=toà chung thẩm+a court exercising final jurisdiction, a court of last resort
